A 30 year old man is set to appear in the Taung magistrate court, North West on Thursday for the alleged murder of his 28 year old girlfriend and 2 year old daughter.The police arrested the man after he handed himself in on Tuesday.According to police the suspect informed them what about the incident and later took the police to the crime scene where they found the victims lying dead inside the house, next to the toilet.The cause of this crime is yet unknown, however the police are investigating.The man is charged with two counts of murder.TNA Reporter